steak is always a winner, but the star of this meal might be the pumpkin-thyme gratin, with a creamy, cheesy sauce and a golden
panko crumb. Grab a fork and dig right in!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
